{"id":383765,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/03/【网络民议】打架就怕遇到神经病啊能不害怕吗/","date":"2015-03-01T10:26:08Z","modified":"2015-11-06T11:27:02Z","title":"【网络民议】打架就怕遇到神经病啊能不害怕吗","content":"<p><strong><a href=\"http://www.chinanews.com/tp/hd2011/2015/02-28/487007.shtml\">中新网｜黑河边防侦察兵零下20度赤膊刀术训练</a></strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>2015年2月27日，黑龙江黑河市，黑龙江省军区某边防团机动步兵连官兵冒着零下20度严寒赤膊进行刀术训练，招招制敌，杀声震天。该连是一支具有红军血脉的连队，尤以战斗作风过硬、敢打硬仗著称。</p></blockquote>\n<p>以下图片来自新浪微博<a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/1371675920/C6tXDudEL\">@安普若-外号安校长</a>：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/03/51c21d10jw1epprn420tsj20qq0gxjv2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-383768\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/03/51c21d10jw1epprn420tsj20qq0gxjv2.jpg\" alt=\"耍刀1\" width=\"525\" height=\"332\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/03/51c21d10jw1epprn420tsj20qq0gxjv2.jpg 962w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/03/51c21d10jw1epprn420tsj20qq0gxjv2-300x190.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/03/51c21d10jw1epprnaarlnj20qq0gm77s.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-383770\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/03/51c21d10jw1epprnaarlnj20qq0gm77s.jpg\" alt=\"耍刀2\" width=\"525\" height=\"326\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/03/51c21d10jw1epprnaarlnj20qq0gm77s.jpg 962w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/03/51c21d10jw1epprnaarlnj20qq0gm77s-300x186.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><br />\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-383772\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/03/51c21d10jw1epprndey20j20qq0hr418.jpg\" alt=\"耍刀3\" width=\"525\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/03/51c21d10jw1epprndey20j20qq0hr418.jpg 962w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/03/51c21d10jw1epprndey20j20qq0hr418-300x199.j